query:
WITH
limiting_table AS (
	SELECT
		  a.join_customer
		 ,  a.join_ts
		 ,  email
		 ,  segment_id
		 ,  first_session_at
		 ,  device
		 ,  session_source
		 ,  session_kind
		 ,  survey_email_captured_at
	FROM (
		SELECT
			 NVL(s.customer, s.source_id) AS  join_customer
			 , s.customer AS  email
			 , s.source_id AS  segment_id
			 , s.ts AS  first_session_at
			 , e.device AS  device
			 , e.session_source AS  session_source
			 , e.session_kind AS  session_kind
			 , s.ts AS  join_ts
		FROM dw.mv_activity_stream AS s
		LEFT OUTER JOIN dw.mv_enriched_pages AS e
			ON ( s.activity_id = e.enriched_activity_id )
		WHERE s.activity = 'session' 
			AND s.ts > '2018-10-01' 
			AND s.activity_occurrence = 1
	) AS a
	JOIN (
		SELECT
			 NVL(s.customer, s.source_id) AS  join_customer
			 , s.ts AS  survey_email_captured_at
			 , s.ts AS  join_ts
		FROM dw.mv_activity_stream AS s
		WHERE s.activity = 'survey_email_captured' 
			AND s.activity_occurrence = 1
	) AS b
		ON (a.join_customer = b.join_customer)
),
pivoted_table AS (
	SELECT
		 NVL(s.customer, s.source_id) AS  join_customer
		 , MIN(s.ts) AS  min_ts
		 , MIN(CASE 
			WHEN s.activity = 'survey_wizard_completed' then s.ts 
			ELSE null
		 END) AS  survey_wizard_completed_at
		 , MIN(CASE 
			WHEN s.activity = 'photos_recieved' then s.ts 
			ELSE null
		 END) AS  photos_received_at
		 , MIN(CASE 
			WHEN s.activity = 'ordered_impression_kit' then s.ts 
			ELSE null
		 END) AS  ordered_impression_kit_at
	FROM dw.mv_activity_stream AS s
	WHERE (s.activity_occurrence = 1 
		AND s.activity IN ('photos_recieved', 'survey_wizard_completed', 'ordered_impression_kit')) 
	GROUP BY NVL(s.customer, s.source_id)
)
SELECT
	  email
	 ,  segment_id
	 ,  first_session_at
	 ,  device
	 ,  session_source
	 ,  session_kind
	 ,  survey_email_captured_at
	 ,  survey_wizard_completed_at
	 ,  photos_received_at
	 ,  name
	 ,  converted_to_survey_wizard_completed
	 ,  ordered_impression_kit_at
	 ,  converted_to_ordered_impression_kit
	 ,  days_from_session_to_ordered_impression_kit
	 ,  session_attribution
	 ,  sa_row_number
	 ,  sa_count
	 ,  sa_percent_of_total
	 ,  categorized_source
	 ,  decimated_session
FROM (
	SELECT
		  email
		 ,  segment_id
		 ,  first_session_at
		 ,  device
		 ,  session_source
		 ,  session_kind
		 ,  survey_email_captured_at
		 ,  survey_wizard_completed_at
		 ,  photos_received_at
		 ,  name
		 ,  ordered_impression_kit_at
		 ,  converted_to_survey_wizard_completed
		 ,  converted_to_ordered_impression_kit
		 ,  days_from_session_to_ordered_impression_kit
		 ,  session_attribution
		 ,  categorized_source
		 ,  decimated_session
		 ,  sa_row_number
		 ,  sa_count
		 , RATIO_TO_REPORT(sa_count) over (partition by session_attribution) AS  sa_percent_of_total
	FROM (
		SELECT
			  email
			 ,  segment_id
			 ,  first_session_at
			 ,  device
			 ,  session_source
			 ,  session_kind
			 ,  survey_email_captured_at
			 ,  survey_wizard_completed_at
			 ,  photos_received_at
			 ,  name
			 ,  ordered_impression_kit_at
			 ,  converted_to_survey_wizard_completed
			 ,  converted_to_ordered_impression_kit
			 ,  days_from_session_to_ordered_impression_kit
			 ,  session_attribution
			 ,  categorized_source
			 ,  decimated_session
			 , ROW_NUMBER() over (partition by session_attribution order by first_session_at) AS  sa_row_number
			 , COUNT(*) over (partition by session_attribution) AS  sa_count
		FROM (
			SELECT
				  email
				 ,  segment_id
				 ,  first_session_at
				 ,  device
				 ,  session_source
				 ,  session_kind
				 ,  survey_email_captured_at
				 ,  survey_wizard_completed_at
				 ,  photos_received_at
				 ,  name
				 ,  ordered_impression_kit_at
				 , CASE 
					WHEN "survey_wizard_completed_at" is NOT NULL THEN 1 
					ELSE 0
				 END AS  converted_to_survey_wizard_completed
				 , CASE 
					WHEN "ordered_impression_kit_at" is NOT NULL THEN 1 
					ELSE 0
				 END AS  converted_to_ordered_impression_kit
				 , DATE_DIFF('days', first_session_at::TIMESTAMP, ordered_impression_kit_at::TIMESTAMP) AS  days_from_session_to_ordered_impression_kit
				 ,  NVL(session_source,'') || ' - ' || NVL(session_kind,'')  AS  session_attribution
				 , CASE 
					WHEN "session_kind" = 'Referral' THEN 'NOT Direct-Organic-Search' 
					WHEN "session_source" = 'Organic' THEN 'Direct-Organic-Search' 
					WHEN "session_kind" is NOT NULL THEN 'is set test' 
					WHEN "session_kind" in ('Direct', 'Search') THEN '****Direct-Organic-Search' 
					ELSE 'NOT Direct-Organic-Search'
				 END AS  categorized_source
				 , DATE_TRUNC('hour', first_session_at::TIMESTAMP) + DATE_PART('minute', first_session_at::TIMESTAMP)::int / 5 * interval '5 minute'  AS  decimated_session
			FROM (
				SELECT
					  email
					 ,  segment_id
					 ,  first_session_at
					 ,  device
					 ,  session_source
					 ,  session_kind
					 ,  survey_email_captured_at
					 ,  survey_wizard_completed_at
					 ,  photos_received_at
					 ,  name
					 ,  ordered_impression_kit_at
				FROM limiting_table AS l
				LEFT OUTER JOIN pivoted_table AS p
					ON (l.join_customer = p.join_customer)
				LEFT OUTER JOIN dw.v_customers AS c
					ON (l.join_customer = c.customer)
			)
		)
	)
)
ORDER BY decimated_session desc
